@Node "Open..."

@{b}   PROJECT MENU Open...@{ub}

 Opens new project to edit and sends parameters to synth. 
 Sends parameters to synth only if set in @{" Serial Prefs " Link "Prefs"}.

  -Opens Program and Effect Parameters if in @{" Program " Link "Program"} or @{" Effect " Link "Effect"} mode.
  -Opens Mix parameters if in @{" Mix " Link "Mix"} mode. 
  -Opens any data if in @{" Capture " Link "Capture"} mode. 

   Files must be in SysEX format if in PROGRAM, EFFECT or MIX mode. If in 
   CAPTURE mode any data less than 524272 bytes long can be loaded and vie-
   wed.  
@EndNode


@Node "Save As..." 

@{b}   PROJECT MENU Save As...@{ub}

 Saves projects parameters. 

  -Saves Program and Effect parameters if in @{" Program " Link "Program"} or @{" Effect " Link "Effect"} mode.
  -Saves Mix parameters if in @{" Mix " Link "Mix"} mode.
  -Saves any data if in @{" Capture " Link "Capture"} mode. 

  If in PROGRAM, EFFECT or MIX mode data is saved in Alesis QS-Series SysEX
  format. 
@EndNode

