@Node "Read This First!"

 Here you can edit all the parameters found on both KEYBOARD and DRUM modes.
 Dragging sliders, clicking cycle gadgets and listview gadgets sends parame-
 ters to synth if serial (or similiar) device opened properly. Gadgets also 
 remember their values if you choose different sound, change to another win-
 dow or change between different modes. 
@EndNode


